----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@JvAVICapture.pas
Summary
    Contains the TJvAVICapture component, a component used to display and capture video streams
  received
    from a source that is compatible with AviCAP. The most common example of such a source is a
  WebCam.
Author
  Olivier Sannier
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvUsedEvents
<TITLE TJvUsedEvents type>
Summary
  The events to trigger if they occur.
Description
  You can decide to activate some events at some times. If you don't they won't be triggered even if
  their associated handler exists. The set is made of these possible values:
  
  <TABLE>
  Value          Meaning
  -------------  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
  ueCapControl   the <LINK TJvAVICapture.OnCapControl, OnCapControl> event will be triggered
  ueError        the <LINK TJvAVICapture.OnError, OnError> event will be triggered
  ueFrame        the <LINK TJvAVICapture.OnFrame, OnFrame> event will be triggered
  ueStatus       the <LINK TJvAVICapture.OnStatus, OnStatus> event will be triggered
  ueVideoStream  the <LINK TJvAVICapture.OnVideoStream, OnVideoStream> event will be
                   triggered
  ueWaveStream   the <LINK TJvAVICapture.OnWaveStream, OnWaveStream> event will be triggered
  ueYield        the <LINK TJvAVICapture.OnYield, OnYield> event will be triggered </TABLE>

