See Also
  TJvAVICapture.PreviewFPS, TJvAVICapture.Previewing

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAVICapture.PreviewFPS
Summary
  The requested number of Frames Per Second for a previewing session.
Description
  Do not set this value too high, as the rendering during a previewing session is done using GDI
  calls, known to be highly CPU demanding.
See Also
  TJvAVICapture.PreviewFrameDelay, TJvAVICapture.Previewing

