  nId    - The id of the status change (see win32 API for more details).
  Str    - The string associated with that status change.
See Also
  TJvAVICapture.UsedEvents

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvAVICapture.OnError
Summary
  The event triggered in case of an error.
