@@TJvAVICapture.FileSizeAlloc
Summary
  The minimum file size for a capture into a file.
Description
  An empty file of that size will be created when capture starts. This prevents the system from
  constantly reallocating space for the capture file and thus saves processing power. When the
  capture is finished, the file size will be truncated to the extent at which the capture required it.
